Replaces: rpicam-apps, libcamera-apps-lite (<< 1.4.1-1~)
Breaks: libcamera-apps-lite (<< 1.4.1-1~)
Description: rpicam-apps-lite
 Small suite of libcamera-based apps that aim to copy the functionality of the
 existing "raspicam" apps. This version excludes features which require X11 and
 Qt

